		(iPhone, iPod Touch, iPad). </p>
		<p>You might not be able to test the app straight away as your device UUID needs 
		to be among those approved to run the application. Once approved, you can proceed. </p>
		<p>2. Start the application and use the following credetials to log in: Email: 
